REC Gets $40 Million for Terminating Long-Term Wafer Contract

-- B y   M a r i a n n e   S t i g s e t
-- 
2011-09-19T06:02:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/rec-gets-40-million-for-terminating-long-term-wafer-contract.html
Renewable Energy Corporation ASA
has agreed to terminate a long-term wafer sales contract and
will receive $40 million cash compensation in the third quarter.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
